{"tid":1519842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚，絕對吾係最後既晚餐！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T02:03:50.000Z","uid":10119,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a35c8cff7e88d1daeb0183093b9c6de3278cb8af","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】六位宗教領袖發聲明，呼籲各界給予香港兩個月「靜止期」，以思考及準備達成平衡各方的共識。<br />\n<br />\n六位宗教領袖座談會成員包括香港佛教聯合會會長寬運法師、天主教香港教區宗座署理湯漢樞機 、孔教學院院長湯恩佳 、中華回教博愛社主席薩智生、香港基督教協進會主席蘇成溢牧師及香港道教聯合會梁德華道長。<br />\n<br />\n他們指眼見當下因修例風波引發連串紛爭，令社會各階層受到嚴重影響，呼籲政府及示威人士讓香港享有兩個月「靜止期」，有機會思考和準備，以整體港人的福祉為目標，達成平衡各方的共識，他們又指願意與各界協調，深盼政府以民為本，市民以香港為家，互相適切回應訴求。<br />\nreference： <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361076&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0oL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=5371fd14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361076&h=0cd2d7b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361076</a><br />\n宗教領袖係唔會企係我地果邊，所以我地係要靠自己企出黎！<br />\n<br />\nreference： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491878/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491878/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n由於警方對聽日（8月31日）嘅遊行發出反對通知書，聽日想出黎，除咗行街之外，仲可以參加「召集十萬基督徒為香港罪人祈禱大&quot;集會&quot;」 (原post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491878/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491878/</a>)。<br />\n為保護呢班60後耶撚，聽日呢個集會必須同耶穌有關。我想呼籲全港基督徒聽日出黎呢個集會傳福音同埋帶未信者祈禱。<br />\n而非耶撚亦可以主動黎&quot;聽福音&quot;同埋一齊祈禱<br />\n聽日用手勢做signal，指定動作(擊掌):<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaJUrn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaJUrn8.jpg&h=bf1ae570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n耶撚：舉左手，我要傳福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未耶撚：舉右手，我要聽福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班非耶撚同我地擊好掌就好乖乖地聽我地班耶撚傳福音喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30770f3fdc818307423543bd564d79b8c826b18","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"依家嘅Popo就好似耶穌時代嘅稅吏，人見人怕<br />\n／／法利賽人中的文士 看見耶穌和罪人並稅吏一同吃飯，就對他門徒說：「他和稅吏並罪人一同吃喝嗎？」 耶穌聽見，就對他們說：「康健的人用不着醫生，有病的人才用得着。我來本不是召義人，乃是召罪人。」（‭‭馬可福音‬ ‭2:16-17）／／<br />\n所以如果大家可以嘅話，唔好吝惜對警犬傳福音嘅機會。因為神愛世人，福音係屬於每一個願意悔改歸向上帝嘅人。<br />\n／／「你們聽見有話說：『當愛你的鄰舍，恨你的仇敵。』 只是我告訴你們，要愛你們的仇敵，為那逼迫你們的禱告。 這樣 就可以作你們天父的兒子；因為他叫日頭照好人，也照歹人；降雨給義人，也給不義的人。 你們若 單 愛那愛你們的人，有甚麼賞賜呢？就是稅吏不也是這樣行嗎？ 你們若單請你弟兄的安，比人有甚麼長處呢？就是外邦人不也是這樣行嗎？ 所以，你們要完全，像你們的天父完全一樣。」（‭‭馬太福音‬ ‭5:43-48）／／<br />\n<br />\n愛敵人不是默不作聲，而容讓他們任意而為。<br />\n對敵人的愛，是可能令對方感到難受的愛。 <br />\n對敵人的愛，就是向著權勢講出真相。<br />\n~Lloyd Pietersen, Does the Matthean Jesus really love his enemies?<br />\n<br />\n聽日可能係世界上同一時間最多人傳同聽福音嘅一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">宗教活動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">基督徒，聽日係你地作光既好機會，將教會帶入世界。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XqOPj456vk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXqOPj456vk4&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0oL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=25654c27\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XqOPj456vk4</a><br />\n／／賜我勇敢的心一無畏懼，因為我願為你去／／<br />\n上帝啊，求你賜我地有一顆勇敢既心，任憑主用。<br />\n<br />\n馬太福音 28:19 <br />\n所以你們要去，使萬民做我的門徒，奉父、子、聖靈的名給他們施洗， 20凡我所吩咐你們的，都教訓他們遵守。我就常與你們同在，直到世界的末了。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<span style=\"color: violet;\"></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">我在這裡，請差遣我</span>。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，附上小弟5年前有幸起街到俾人傳福音既小冊子一直keep到依家，歡迎各位基督徒同未信者用黎傳福音用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfNh8v4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfNh8v4.jpg&h=f79288ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BA334q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BA334q.jpg&h=487aff48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W0riSXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW0riSXL.jpg&h=167286fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fky1QKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFky1QKq.jpg&h=3f13a379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMMyGQ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMMyGQ6.jpg&h=02e79af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6MScXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6MScXM.jpg&h=c42869ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5222a8a661e7ee67984fc405b017dc1ff770afda","tid":1519842,"uid":197535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"831 end game?<br />\n你忍唔住就真係end game la<br />\ngear 都唔洗 因為係全人和理be water<br />\n9月仲要同狗仔玩<br />\n10月1仲要全港人人護旗慶回歸"},{"pid":"1534240c9e1281538895ebd27485167e87240708","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2d0f19c79e1747aec203098640630fe93a76b7","tid":1519842,"uid":150848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:06:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"142ea44ae26b35a3fc196f633a49cef1f0e2ca47","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"分左2頁終於出到post喇!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f2ccc3320a6e4f0cd8a1a499ae80180ffe63e2","tid":1519842,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1</a><br />\n為了防止狗賊唔比搵律師，請各位義士發夢之前搵一個信得過既家人或者朋友交低一個時間，例如我今日去夢遊, 若果我在夜晚2200之前無報平安, 就等於出左事, 要搵律師。地點可能有少少麻煩, 要走幾轉先知, 但係都好過比人拉48個鐘。當然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/5nobb2zmllj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F5nobb2zmllj31.jpg&h=7e932cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fxz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg&h=b31178b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/hb6qnadvjkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fhb6qnadvjkj31.jpg&h=d5f45a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c94939d4c0693631a663c5c38ad5fb4670b3c04","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"推呀!!!!"},{"pid":"0fbf735cbc08bbee85379135505881dd1cc5227e","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"好好用福音保護自己呀!!得宗教集會係不需反對！！！！"},{"pid":"9b764001705e945b1f5ce824a68befbdda708b98","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"好好用福音保護自己呀!!得宗教集會係不需反對！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bf289f2fd1d66a0ca2268b5dcd551c9df96b60","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"自推！！！！好好用福音同祈禱保護自己呀!!得宗教集會係不需反對！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8a4ce578af2d52ff80619ea63c19a39b04efc0","tid":1519842,"uid":10119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit